4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper involves the construction of codes based on classical constacyclic MDS codes, which may involve the use of algorithms and data structures. 
5. cs.SD (Sound) - This sub-category is less likely, but the paper may involve the use of sound theory in the construction of the codes.
